-first-games-showcase-here-at-1pm-et-163024545.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 71ed3148-1583-4354-9099-2b2f226ded56</guid><dc:creator>斯蒂芬妮·巴恩斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 16:30:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693251543</ingested><modified> 2023-08-28T19:39:07+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Stephanie Barnes]]></category><media:content height="386" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8dd25100-45d7-11ee-9ffa-a1e74d362bef" width="686"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="386" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8dd25100-45d7-11ee-9ffa-a1e74d362bef" width="686"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Panic]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Panic Games Showcase]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Panic Games Showcase]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple's iPhone 15 event is set for September 12th]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>厌倦了告诉你的朋友和家人现在不要购买 iPhone 14？我也是，所以这方面有一些好消息：<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/apple/">苹果</a>已经确定了 9 月份年度活动的日期，在此期间我们肯定会了解<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/iphone-15/">iPhone 15</a>系列以及其他设备新版本的所有信息。您可以设置美国东部时间 9 月 12 日下午 1 点的日历提醒，提醒自己返回 Engadget 观看直播。</p><p>几乎去年的活动一结束，有关苹果为 iPhone 15 系列准备什么的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-solid-state-buttons-ming-chi-kuo-083518207.html">谣言就开始流传</a>。所有型号（也许除了新的 SE 之外）都可以<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/all-iphone-15-models-will-reportedly-feature-dynamic-island-cutouts-222957434.html">放弃刘海</a>并开始使用<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-iphone-14-pro-max-review-dynamic-island-useful-always-on-display-battery-life-camera-test-sample-pictures-130020449.html">iPhone 14 Pro 和 Pro Max</a>中首次亮相的动态岛切口。然而，如果您想要<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/wifi-6e-could-be-one-of-the-features-apple-uses-to-differentiate-iphone-15-pro-models-193640691.html">WiFi 6E 连接</a>而不是 WiFi 6，您可能需要选择 iPhone 15 Pro。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/iphone-15-pro-set-to-feature-a-thinner-bezel-titanium-frame-and-usb-c-charging-094118389.html">有报道称</a>15 Pro 和 Pro Max 将会有更薄的边框和钛金属框架，但我们可能要等到明年才能看到<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-may-introduce-a-pricier-iphone-ultra-next-year-172301607.html">传闻中的 iPhone Ultra</a> 。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/38658d20-4688-11ee-b78d-606a73bd384b" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/38658d20-4688-11ee-b78d-606a73bd384b" style="height:810px;width:1350px;" alt="2023 年 9 月 Apple 活动邀请。图片显示波浪状的苹果标志像风中的沙子一样消散。文本：" data-uuid="f92771c2-d49b-37a1-a79f-61d7356f7b38"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">苹果</div></figure><p>最有趣的是，苹果可能最终会开始在 iPhone 15 系列中逐步淘汰 Lightning 端口，并转向期待已久的 USB-C。该公司在那里没有太多选择，因为<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/eu-usb-c-wired-charging-deadline-152454857.html">从明年开始，</a>在欧盟销售的所有平板电脑和智能手机都需要使用该充电端口。对于苹果来说，为所有新设备使用相同的连接器将更加简单，而不是试图在其他市场坚持使用闪电端口。</p><p>无论如何，我们不必等待太久就能了解今年新款 iPhone 的全部信息。我们很可能也会了解 Apple Watch 的下一步发展。苹果也总有可能推出“one more thing”惊喜。与往常一样，我们将全面报道今年秋季 iPhone 发布会的情况。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apples-iphone-15-event-is-set-for-september-12th-161028116.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apples-iphone-15-event-is-set-for-september-12th-161028116.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 173c0538-c63b-4534-8e92-18bb3fb7158d</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 16:10:54 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693326245</ingested><modified> 2023-08-29T16:24:08+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Smart Phones]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-09/4c013cb0-33da-11ed-ba6d-6dd962e11892" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1333" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-09/4c013cb0-33da-11ed-ba6d-6dd962e11892" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Cherlynn Low / Engadget]]></me