们。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/96e78a40-4662-11ee-b7f4-ad88dd197592" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/96e78a40-4662-11ee-b7f4-ad88dd197592" style="height:800px;width:426px;" alt="Google 相册的屏幕截图，其中显示了一个页面，您可以在其中选择是否备份锁定的文件夹。" data-uuid="25767e6b-1def-30fe-9c20-c2515e904dcd"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">谷歌</div></figure><p>谷歌还开始推出照片应用程序的简化设置页面。当用户单击其帐户图标并检查设置页面时，他们现在将看到一个新的布局，使他们可以通过导航新的隐私、备份、共享和通知部分更轻松地找到所需的内容。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/google-photos-now-lets-you-access-and-set-up-locked-folders-on-ios-and-the-web-150044373 .html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/google-photos-now-lets-you-access-and-set-up-locked-folders-on-ios-and-the-web-150044373.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 3f475e4f-2a52-481a-adff-43dbddb1243c</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 29 Aug 2023 15:00:44 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693310618</ingested><modified> 2023-08-29T12:03:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="4016" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/d7624350-4660-11ee-95fd-394fb219f6bf" width="6016"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media